            </h2>

            <p class="contentpheight">
                <hr class="hrp">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home blueGoldBorderSM f15"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Residential service companies<br /><hr class="hrp">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home blueGoldBorderSM f15"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Regions and municipalities<br /><hr class="hrp">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home blueGoldBorderSM f15"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Manufacturing companies<br /><hr class="hrp">
